## üß† Scenario Summary
Glitch's reverse shell has gone silent‚Äîhis connection to the home base was hijacked. Mayor Malware‚Äôs minions have modified the shellcode, redirecting it to the wrong IP and port. Your mission is to patch the shellcode with the correct values and reestablish control over the digital vault.

